def: Early fruit or vegetables; especially, early pease. Mortimer.
Of or pertaining to the millennium, or to a thousand years; as,a millennial period; millennial happiness.
According to measure or proportion; proportionable;proportionate. [Obs.]
State of being paired with a single mate.
A dipterous larva used as fish bait.
Having three prongs; trident; tridentate; as, a tridented mace.[R.] Quarles.
A genus of umbelliferous plants somewhat like thistles inappearance. Eryngium maritimum, or sea holly, has been highlyesteemed as an aphrodisiac, the roots being formerly candied.
A genus of grasses, including several hundred species, some ofwhich are valuable; panic grass.
A prefix used adjectively and adverbially in the sense ofamiss, wrong, ill, wrongly, unsuitably; as, misdeed, mislead,mischief, miscreant.
